# Email via Fastmail JMAP over HTTPS/443. SMTP (465/587) is BLOCKED on the
# DigitalOcean droplet — see JMAP_EMAIL.md. The token is a Fastmail *API token*
# (Settings -> Privacy & Security -> API tokens), NOT the IMAP/SMTP app password.
FASTMAIL_API_TOKEN=fmu1-your-api-token
COMPLIANCE_FROM_EMAIL=compliance@npedwards.com
COMPLIANCE_TO_EMAIL=nick.edwards1988@gmail.com

